data.description: Introducing a Timeless Treasure: Historic 1927 stucco home nestled amidst the serene charm of Milwaukie.  This charming residence stands as a testament to a bygone era offering the perfect balance between history and comfort. Hardwood floors offer warmth while the elegant stairway beckons you to explore all that this home has to offer. The spacious living room has character and features a cozy fireplace framed by period-specific accents. The dining room is bathed in natural light and is ideal for hosting intimate gatherings or elaborate dinner parties. This home offers plenty of space for family and guests and features unique charm. Large tree-shaded lot that's perfect for outdoor entertaining, gardening, or simply unwinding in the beauty of nature. The detached double car garage provides both convenience and storage options.  If you are not afraid to do your own updates, this could be the property for you!
